videos.headline: SMU connects on 7-yard TD
videos.description: SMU QB Ben Hicks fakes a handoff and hits Ryan Becker in the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Houston QB launches 50-yard TD pass
videos.description: Houston QB D'Eriq King airs out a long pass and hits Marquez Stevenson in stride for a 50-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Houston scoops up fumble for TD
videos.description: SMU's Xavier Jones coughs up the ball and Gleson Sprewell returns it 24 yards for a Houston touchdown.

videos.headline: SMU scores before 1st half ends
videos.description: Ben Hicks swings a pass to James Proche for a short touchdown with seconds remaining in the 2nd quarter.
